4075	4192	h	99152	1129	2022-03-08 18:22:57.040524	2022-04-08 03:42:33.51171	Fracturing	Pressure process whereby ice is permanently deformed, and rupture oc- curs. Most commonly used to describe breaking across very close pack ice, compact pack ice, and consolidated pack ice. 	\N	h4192	published	vernacular	\N	\N
