4106	4223	h	99152	1129	2022-03-08 18:23:01.344468	2022-04-08 03:42:33.51171	Freezing spray	Freezing spray occurs when a combination of below freezing temperatures and strong winds, causes a wind-generated spray to freeze and accumulate (or build-up) on any marine infrastructure located in or near the vicinity of the water. 	\N	h4223	published	vernacular	\N	\N
